---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      Raoni Andrade, a software developer from Brazil.
      <br />
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      A <b class="font-bold">native Portuguese</b> speaker, <b class="font-bold">fluent in English</b>, <b class="font-bold">intermediate in Spanish</b>, and with a <b class="font-bold">foundation in Dutch/Flemish</b>.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      What truly sets me apart is my resilience. I excel at working with diverse teams, embracing a wide range of opinions, backgrounds, and beliefs. I genuinely believe that the most valuable growth occurs within diversity and the unknown.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      While I have some preferred tools, I always choose the best one for the
      job, even if it's not on my usual list. My goal is to find the right
      solution for each project.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
